Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: First primary in presidential campaign
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b03z99d7
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 29 Feb 1976
First primary in election campaign. Results show only who the losers are, no indication of eventual winner. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less